  %% Diagram 63: PRISM Academy Learning and Certification Progress Flow

  Enroll[Vendor enrolls in academy module]
  Track[Track progress events in academy_progress]
  Inactive{No progress for reminder window?}
  Reminder[Send reminder and re-engagement nudges]
  Resume[Vendor resumes learning path]

  Complete{Module completed?}

  Continue[Continue lesson path]
  Prereq{All prerequisites complete?}
  Cert[Issue certification]
  Unlock[Unlock badge, feature prompts, and milestone benefits]

  Block[Block certification]

  Enroll --> Track --> Inactive
  Inactive -- Yes --> Reminder --> Resume --> Track
  Inactive -- No --> Complete

  Complete -- No --> Continue --> Track
  Complete -- Yes --> Prereq

  Prereq -- Yes --> Cert --> Unlock
  Prereq -- No --> Block --> Reminder --> Track
